SPEAKER 1: Welcome to the
2018 Android Developer Summit.

00:00:07.410 --> 00:00:10.710
This is an event for
developers by developers.

00:00:16.530 --> 00:00:22.380
SPEAKER 2: With over 2 billion
devices, 3/4 of a trillion apps

00:00:22.380 --> 00:00:25.290
downloaded every year,
Android's developer community

00:00:25.290 --> 00:00:26.610
is growing hugely.

00:00:26.610 --> 00:00:31.810
We saw it more than double
just in the past few years.

00:00:31.810 --> 00:00:35.520
SPEAKER 3: So the Android App
Bundle makes it much simpler.

00:00:35.520 --> 00:00:38.220
