developer work needed,

00:00:38.220 --> 00:00:42.420
the App Bundle now makes
apps an average of 8% smaller

00:00:42.420 --> 00:00:45.234
to download for m+ devices.

00:00:45.234 --> 00:00:46.650
SPEAKER 4: So a
few months ago, we

00:00:46.650 --> 00:00:49.200
announced Jetpack, the next
generation of Android tools

00:00:49.200 --> 00:00:52.680
