00:01:08.970 --> 00:01:12.000
reducing the number of crashes,
hangs, and memory leaks;

00:01:12.000 --> 00:01:14.730
fixing user-impacting bugs; and
investing our infrastructure

00:01:14.730 --> 00:01:15.570
and tools.

00:01:15.570 --> 00:01:18.450
We're bringing the full power
of Android Studio to Chrome OS

00:01:18.450 --> 00:01:20.130
early next year.

00:01:20.130 --> 00:01:23.010
